### Create a New Task
POST http://localhost:4000/tasks
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Complete assignment",
  "description": "Finish the math assignment",
  "due_date": "2024-12-01",
  "category": "School"
}

###

### Get All Tasks
GET http://localhost:4000/tasks

###

### Update a Task
PUT http://localhost:4000/tasks/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "title": "Complete updated assignment",
  "description": "Finish the updated math assignment",
  "due_date": "2024-12-15",
  "category": "Updated School"
}

###

### Mark a Task as Completed
PATCH http://localhost:4000/tasks/1/complete

###

### Delete a Task
DELETE http://localhost:4000/tasks/3
